---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Elissa" description="About Elissa (aka pingu/blahai)">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						My name is Elissa and I am an 18 year old trans girl from Finland.
						I was born in 2006. My egg cracked in the summer of 2022
						and came out to my family a few months later. 
					</p>
					<p>
						I first started using Linux in 2020. I started off by jumping straight into the deep end
						and installed Arch Linux after not even a week of trying out Ubuntu. Of course knowing
						pretty much nothing about Linux I had to learn a lot but I'd be lying if I said it wasn't a lot of fun.
						A few years into using Arch as my daily driver I was introduced to NixOS which I got really excited about.
						Now I dualboot Arch and Nix because I still love Arch and truth be told it is a lot easier than nix. 
					</p>
					<p>
						Somewhere around 2022 I bought my first VPS and ever since then I've been hooked on servers and self hosting.
						My dream job would be working as a sysadmin, and run my own homelab. 
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						I am currently studying in upper secondar high school and will graduate in 2025.
				 	</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						I have a lot of experience in system management and tools like docker.
						I only have a bit of experience in programming any big projects but I am pretty good at scripting.

					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
